{
  "stem": "6719.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And today you have a mixture of, uh, new Canadians and very old Canadian, but young people, mostly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, you know, the old ones are dying out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Most of them are dead anyhow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There are just a few around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a printer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father wrote articles for-- for-- for some of the, uh, social democratic newspapers, always, uh, anti-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to have fights with-- he used to belong to a group of people that were-- you know, the other day we were talking about.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In German-- or in Austrian-- it was called a [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Schutzbund ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think that if you translate it, it was called marshals, you know, that-- that took care of their own.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a demonstration or there was something like that, these were the people that protected the people that were demonstrating, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, uh, they always had fights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They used to fight with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to fight with, uh, what we used to call the, uh-- the [? schwarzen ?] the black ones, which was the conservatives.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Uh, and, uh, I remember one time, when he came home and his-- he always wore white shirts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is always in my mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, uh, it was full of blood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother was carrying on and he says, just wash it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's-- that's the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And also I remember another incident that I-- that I didn't talk to you about, and that was in Vienna there is something like in, uh-- in-- in-- in Scandinavia and Denmark, like Tivoli Garden.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's called a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There is the ferris wheel, which is usually in pictures when you look at Vienna, and you know, you see the church and you see a ferris wheel.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
